---
title: Pan-fried Chive Butter Salmon with roast potatoes and broccoli
description: Rich and creamy chive butter sauce in this recipe is the perfect complement to soft and flaky fried salmon. The roasted potatoes and veg on the side make for a well rounded and delicious dish.
